    <text>
        <body>

        <p><span facs="#zone_f11a11f4-c383-11e8-b200-f40f243b5e05">昭和三年一月十五日</span><span facs="#zone_f11a1652-c383-11e8-9907-f40f243b5e05">工學會理事長</span><span facs="#zone_f11a18dc-c383-11e8-85e5-f40f243b5e05">男爵</span><span facs="#zone_f11a1b14-c383-11e8-b143-f40f243b5e05">古市公威</span><span facs="#zone_f11a1d34-c383-11e8-9671-f40f243b5e05">「</span><span facs="#zone_f11a1f08-c383-11e8-811f-f40f243b5e05">あ殿</span><span facs="#zone_f11a20e6-c383-11e8-829b-f40f243b5e05">謹啓時下益々御健勝放賀至極に存候</span><span facs="#zone_f11a22c0-c383-11e8-a1bb-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a23fe-c383-11e8-a515-f40f243b5e05">陳者日本鋼業管</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2514-c383-11e8-9cde-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2624-c383-11e8-9573-f40f243b5e05">日本鐵鋼協會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a273e-c383-11e8-9ddf-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a284a-c383-11e8-8549-f40f243b5e05">土木學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2958-c383-11e8-b647-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2a66-c383-11e8-a8d2-f40f243b5e05">火</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2b74-c383-11e8-810e-f40f243b5e05">兵學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2c82-c383-11e8-b73f-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2d9c-c383-11e8-94a6-f40f243b5e05">造船協會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2ea8-c383-11e8-8127-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a2fc0-c383-11e8-aaa5-f40f243b5e05">建築學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a30da-c383-11e8-8095-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a31f8-c383-11e8-b4ad-f40f243b5e05">工業化學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3312-c383-11e8-a1e6-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3428-c383-11e8-9b33-f40f243b5e05">衛生工業協會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3542-c383-11e8-a8e7-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a365a-c383-11e8-a64b-f40f243b5e05">電気學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3774-c383-11e8-8d6e-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a388a-c383-11e8-8b8d-f40f243b5e05">電信電話學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3998-c383-11e8-b027-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3ab0-c383-11e8-986d-f40f243b5e05">機械學會</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3bd2-c383-11e8-925f-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3cec-c383-11e8-a54b-f40f243b5e05">照明學會を會員として組織せる本官は政府を始め朝野大方の御援助の下に</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3e0a-c383-11e8-8a21-f40f243b5e05">昭和四年秋季をトし東京市に於て萬國工業會議を催すこと</span><span facs="#zone_f11a3f24-c383-11e8-9a22-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4046-c383-11e8-921f-f40f243b5e05">し既に過般諸外國に向け</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4168-c383-11e8-8d61-f40f243b5e05">別期の藤告を發表致候</span><span facs="#zone_f11a428a-c383-11e8-9624-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a43a2-c383-11e8-8168-f40f243b5e05">就ては別紙會議規則に依り今回悠々實施機器を組織致度候に</span><span facs="#zone_f11a44ba-c383-11e8-bb74-f40f243b5e05">付貴下を煩はし右規則所定の評議員として御助力相願度存候</span><span facs="#zone_f11a45d2-c383-11e8-be79-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a46e8-c383-11e8-8e49-f40f243b5e05">申上る迄も無く本施設</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4814-c383-11e8-bb6e-f40f243b5e05">は本邦として創始のここにも有之出来得る丈け有終の美を収め度儀に御座候間御多用</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4938-c383-11e8-9810-f40f243b5e05">の嘘甚た御迷惑の儀とは存候得共何卒御諒承を賜り本會議の爲め折角御援助に預り度</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4a50-c383-11e8-bcf9-f40f243b5e05">右御依賴迄如斯御座候</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4b68-c383-11e8-9727-f40f243b5e05">敬</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4c88-c383-11e8-bdaf-f40f243b5e05">具</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4dac-c383-11e8-ab28-f40f243b5e05">追て作早速本月二十八日</span><span facs="#zone_f11a4eec-c383-11e8-952b-f40f243b5e05">(</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5010-c383-11e8-b4f5-f40f243b5e05">土</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5124-c383-11e8-aa06-f40f243b5e05">)</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5248-c383-11e8-812b-f40f243b5e05">午後二時麹町区永楽町二ノー</span><span facs="#zone_f11a536c-c383-11e8-9c76-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5494-c383-11e8-9197-f40f243b5e05">日本工業倶楽部</span><span facs="#zone_f11a55e2-c383-11e8-9164-f40f243b5e05">(</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5702-c383-11e8-b02f-f40f243b5e05">電話</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5824-c383-11e8-9508-f40f243b5e05">丸ノ内一五四〇</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5930-c383-11e8-8d70-f40f243b5e05">、</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5a54-c383-11e8-8774-f40f243b5e05">一五四六</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5b76-c383-11e8-8620-f40f243b5e05">)</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5cac-c383-11e8-a486-f40f243b5e05">に於て第一回評議員管相催候間本文の御諾否と共に御</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5dc2-c383-11e8-a4e3-f40f243b5e05">出席の有無御垂示被下度向は本計画に関する経過の概要は別紙の通に有之候御参考</span><span facs="#zone_f11a5ee6-c383-11e8-9885-f40f243b5e05">として供清覧候</span></p></body>
